          <li>Wine, beer, and beverage pairing recommendations</li>
          <li>Recipe scaling and conversion calculators</li>
          <li>Party planning and food quantity calculators</li>
          <li>Cooking time and temperature guides</li>
          <li>Nutritional information and dietary tools</li>
